literals.name: nohref

This indicates that the area has no active link.

literals.name: circle

The shape is a circle.
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=0

literals.name: default

This specifies the fact that the area covers the rest of the figure.

literals.name: poly

The area is specified as polygon.

literals.name: rect

enumerations.name: GraphicFitEnum
enumerations.note: This enumerator specifies the policy how to place and scale the figure on the page. Aggregated by Graphic.editfit, Graphic.fit, Graphic.htmlFit

literals.name: AsIs
literals.description:
This indicates that the image shall be incorporated as is without scaling, rotation etc.
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=0

literals.name: AUTOSAR
literals.description:
FO R23-11 FitToText fit to the text containing the graphic.
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=2

literals.name: LimitToPage
literals.description:
This indicates that the width of the graphic shall be limited to the page width. The image shall not be scaled down but cropped.
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=3

literals.name: LimitToText
literals.description:
This indicates that the width of the graphic shall be limited to the width of the current text flow. The image shall not be scaled down but cropped.
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=4

literals.name: Rotate90CcwFitToTextRotate90CcwLimit
literals.description:
Rotate by 90 degree counter clock wise and then fit to text
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=8

literals.name: Rotate90CwFitToTextRotate90CwLimitTo
literals.description:
Rotate by 90 degree and then fit to text
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=11

enumerations.name: GraphicNotationEnum
enumerations.note: This enumerator specifies the various notations (finally file types) used to represent the figure. Aggregated by Graphic.notation

literals.name: AUTOSAR
literals.description:
FO R23-11 svg scalable vector graphic
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=6
